WEBVTT

00:01:28.485 --> 00:01:32.761
I called my best friend, Claire, and said,

00:01:33.578 --> 00:01:36.737
"I know this is going to sound crazy,

00:01:36.761 --> 00:01:38.825
but, um ...

00:01:38.849 --> 00:01:43.828
I think there's a ghost in my house,
and I need to get rid of it."

00:01:43.852 --> 00:01:48.200
And she said -- she's very
open-minded -- and she said,

00:01:48.224 --> 00:01:49.729
"I don't think you're crazy.

00:01:49.753 --> 00:01:53.627
I think you just need
to do a cleansing ritual."

